stolen medical equipment.

14:28.750 --> 14:30.380
At least twenty grand worth,

14:30.380 --> 14:31.960
which makes it
a major felony.

14:31.960 --> 14:33.170
How'd you guys
find out about me?

14:34.540 --> 14:35.790
Come on!

14:35.790 --> 14:38.420
Somebody gave me up.

14:38.420 --> 14:40.250
I'm too smart to get caught
any other way.

14:40.250 --> 14:42.790
But are you smart enough to walk
out of this room a free man?

14:45.540 --> 14:46.580
What are you doing?

14:46.580 --> 14:47.880
Offering up a deal.

14:47.880 --> 14:49.580
But this is a good arrest.

14:49.580 --> 14:52.040
But there's a better one
right up the food chain.

14:52.040 --> 14:53.670
Isn't that right, Chuy?

14:53.670 --> 14:55.620
Maybe.

14:55.620 --> 14:58.120
Make that a "yes," you might
sleep in your own bed tonight.

15:01.080 --> 15:03.250
I'm just saying New York cops
would've, you know,

15:03.250 --> 15:04.880
shown me a little bit
of a better time by now.

15:04.880 --> 15:07.000
If you're unhappy with
the quality of your ride along,

15:07.000 --> 15:08.460
please feel free
to request another unit.

15:08.460 --> 15:11.170
Look, I'm not happy.
You're not happy, either.

15:11.170 --> 15:12.540
You don't want to be taking

15:12.540 --> 15:14.250
these low-risk calls
any more than I do.

15:14.250 --> 15:15.750
With all due respect, I don't
think you could handle

15:15.750 --> 15:17.750
high-stakes calls.

15:17.750 --> 15:19.670
No, just an observation.

15:19.670 --> 15:22.080
I've seen one of your movies.
What, you didn't like it?

15:22.080 --> 15:24.210
It was fine. It just had nothing
to do with real cop work.

15:24.210 --> 15:25.460
Dispatch: 7-Adam-15,

15:25.460 --> 15:28.380
we have a 415
at 9386 9th Avenue.

15:28.380 --> 15:29.620
What's a 415?

15:29.620 --> 15:31.290
Family disturbance.

15:31.290 --> 15:33.790
Probably just
a loud argument.

15:33.790 --> 15:35.120
It's not that far from here.

15:38.210 --> 15:40.580
7-Adam-15 responding.

15:40.580 --> 15:42.330
Yeah.

15:42.330 --> 15:44.040
-No!
-Everybody makes mistakes, bro.
-Relax.

15:44.040 --> 15:45.670
-No! Shut up!
-It's cool. Just chill.

15:45.670 --> 15:46.670
- No! Go!
-Ty.

15:46.670 --> 15:48.040
Tyson:

15:48.040 --> 15:49.580
Malcolm: Yo, you're scaring her,
man, come on.

15:49.580 --> 15:52.580
Everybody makes mistakes.
Just chill.

15:52.580 --> 15:54.000
Finally, some action.

15:54.000 --> 15:55.710
You, stay.
Tyson: No!

15:55.710 --> 15:57.500
-Ty, Ty, it'll be okay.
-Shut up!

15:57.500 --> 15:59.290
Everybody, put your hands
where I can see them.

15:59.290 --> 16:00.880
Tyson:

16:00.880 --> 16:02.790
Malcolm: Go. Go. Hey, back off.
We don't need you here.
Go!

16:02.790 --> 16:04.250
Hey, Ma, I told you
not to call the cops.

16:04.250 --> 16:06.500
-No! No! Go away!
-Yo, they gonna shoot him!

16:06.500 --> 16:07.750
-Nobody's shooting anybody.
-Go!

16:07.750 --> 16:10.080
Everybody, put your hands
where I can see them now.

16:10.080 --> 16:12.170
Tyson: Go away!

16:12.170 --> 16:13.250
Talia: Now.

16:15.170 --> 16:16.620
Knife!

16:16.620 --> 16:19.210
Put the knife down!
Sir, drop the weapon now.

16:19.210 --> 16:21.620
No! No! No! No! No! No!
Wait, wait, wait!

16:21.620 --> 16:22.500
Put the knife down!

16:27.790 --> 16:29.830
Put the weapon down now!
I need you to put
the knife down now.

16:29.830 --> 16:31.420
Don't shoot him.
Don't shoot him.
Tyson, it's okay.

16:31.420 --> 16:33.210
Put down the knife, please.

16:33.210 --> 16:35.170
I did bad.
Tyson did bad.

16:35.170 --> 16:36.880
Nolan: Sir, we are just
here to help you,

16:36.880 --> 16:38.880
but we can't help
until you drop that knife.
Tyson: Go. Go!

16:38.880 --> 16:42.500
He doesn't understand. Please.

16:42.500 --> 16:44.790
He's not gonna hurt anyone.
He's only a child.
Tyson:

16:44.790 --> 16:46.330
He doesn't know how big he is.
-Look, I won't let you hurt him.

16:46.330 --> 16:47.580
I need you
to step back now.

16:47.580 --> 16:49.000
Everyone,
take it down a notch.

16:49.000 --> 16:51.540
-Ty. Ty.

16:51.540 --> 16:53.830
He got confused. The alarm.

16:53.830 --> 16:55.420
I-I shouldn't
have yelled at him.

16:55.420 --> 16:56.830
Could somebody take care
of that alarm?

16:56.830 --> 17:03.960
♪♪

17:05.830 --> 17:08.250
I'm sorry, Momma,
I'm so sorry --

17:08.250 --> 17:11.920
It's okay, baby. I know you
didn't mean to hurt me.

17:11.920 --> 17:15.080
I know!

17:15.080 --> 17:16.880
I burnt the pancakes.

17:16.880 --> 17:19.000
I burnt the pancakes.

17:19.000 --> 17:22.460
Looks like you didn't
flip them in time.

17:22.460 --> 17:25.330
I forgot. I forgot.
I forgot!

17:25.330 --> 17:28.460
I do that sometimes, too.
You know?

17:28.460 --> 17:29.500
Forget when to flip them.

17:31.210 --> 17:33.460
You want to know
a little trick?

17:33.460 --> 17:34.420
How to know
when to flip 'em?

17:37.170 --> 17:38.880
You remember
the little bubbles on top?

17:41.080 --> 17:42.040
Hmm?

17:45.790 --> 17:47.000
When you see those little
bubbles on top,

17:47.000 --> 17:48.080
you know it's time.

17:49.540 --> 17:51.580
Okay?

17:51.580 --> 17:53.000
Okay.

17:53.000 --> 17:55.080
I need you to put
down the knife, Tyson.

17:58.000 --> 18:00.170
Now. Okay?

18:00.170 --> 18:08.620
♪♪

18:08.620 --> 18:10.420
Sorry...

18:10.420 --> 18:12.620
It's okay.
-It's all right.

18:13.830 --> 18:18.040
Isn't public urination
usually a citation?

18:18.040 --> 18:20.000
You need to brush up on your
California Penal Code.

18:20.000 --> 18:21.500
Section 314.

18:21.500 --> 18:23.170
Indecent exposure
is a misdemeanor

18:23.170 --> 18:24.250
subject to six months
in jail.

18:24.250 --> 18:25.540
Hmm.

18:27.040 --> 18:30.330
Indecent exposure
requires an offended party.

18:30.330 --> 18:32.170
Plenty of offended families
living in the apartment building

18:32.170 --> 18:33.380
across that alley.

18:33.380 --> 18:35.330
Mm.

18:35.330 --> 18:37.830
Respectfully, sir,
that'll never stick.

18:39.290 --> 18:41.960
It doesn't matter.
Start processing.

18:41.960 --> 18:43.620
Hey.

18:43.620 --> 18:47.380
Do you want me to give you
a shout if I see the detectives?

18:47.380 --> 18:48.250
Yeah.

18:52.290 --> 18:54.040
Open cell three for me.

19:11.670 --> 19:13.460
I screwed up.

19:13.460 --> 19:15.830
You think?

19:17.620 --> 19:19.710
How bad is it?

19:19.710 --> 19:21.120
It's a solid arrest.

19:23.080 --> 19:26.210
Who's Carson Holland?

19:26.210 --> 19:28.250
The car you were driving
is registered to him.

19:28.250 --> 19:29.380
Is he your boyfriend?

19:31.000 --> 19:32.420
Sometimes.

19:36.040 --> 19:37.790
Okay, you have to tell them
the drugs belong to him.

19:37.790 --> 19:39.380
We both know
it won't matter.

19:39.380 --> 19:42.040
I was in possession.

19:42.040 --> 19:43.830
Isn't there something
you can do?

19:43.830 --> 19:45.330
What?!
They won't drop the charge.

19:45.330 --> 19:47.170
It's connected to
a DEA case.

19:47.170 --> 19:48.830
This is real, Isabel.

19:48.830 --> 19:50.290
It's gonna get worse.

19:50.290 --> 19:51.920
Because tomorrow,
they're gonna have a warrant

19:51.920 --> 19:53.000
to search my apartment.

19:53.000 --> 19:54.120
What will they find?

19:59.710 --> 20:02.540
Carson stashed a kilo of heroin
in my heating unit.

20:03.960 --> 20:05.380
Are you --

20:05.380 --> 20:07.420
Are you that far gone?

20:07.420 --> 20:08.710
Why would you
let him do that?

20:08.710 --> 20:10.880
All right, I will not be able
to plea out of this.

20:10.880 --> 20:12.960
So, i-if I go to jail,

20:12.960 --> 20:15.420
they're gonna find out I was
a cop, and I'll be dead.

20:15.420 --> 20:18.040
Please, baby.
Go -- Go to my place.

20:18.040 --> 20:19.920
I need you.

20:19.920 --> 20:22.790
If you help me, it'll be
different, all right?

20:22.790 --> 20:24.380
I'll go to rehab.

20:24.380 --> 20:26.540
For real this time.
You're just saying that.

20:26.540 --> 20:28.790
No, no, this is different.
I ca-- I can be different.

20:28.790 --> 20:30.750
Please...

20:30.750 --> 20:33.750
help me. Okay?

20:33.750 --> 20:36.670
Please.

20:36.670 --> 20:38.790
7-Adam-15 requesting
an additional unit

20:38.790 --> 20:41.170
for a 51-50 hold.

20:41.170 --> 20:42.170
Hey, y'all
can let him go now.

20:42.170 --> 20:43.580
Momma not pressing
no more charges.

20:43.580 --> 20:45.580
-That's right.
-I'm sorry,

20:45.580 --> 20:47.330
but we have no leeway here.
An assault was committed.

20:47.330 --> 20:48.460
Nolan: But we're not
taking him to jail.

20:48.460 --> 20:50.380
A doctor will evaluate
his needs.

20:50.380 --> 20:52.830
Depending on the diagnosis, he
may even qualify for a facility.

20:52.830 --> 20:54.170
We can't afford that.

20:55.830 --> 20:57.750
Hey, what you doing, brah?

20:57.750 --> 20:59.750
What the hell you doing?
Put that camera away, brah.

20:59.750 --> 21:01.420
No, no, no, it's okay.
I'm -- I'm a director.

21:01.420 --> 21:02.500
This is -- This is so
compelling.

21:02.500 --> 21:04.830
-Rupert, put the camera away.

21:04.830 --> 21:07.540
What, you think my brother's
pain is entertaining

21:07.540 --> 21:09.170
-Step back. Step back.
-Put the camera away.

21:09.170 --> 21:11.170
Step back. Hey.
You don't hear me, brah?
I said put the camera away!

21:11.170 --> 21:14.580
You think I'm playing with you?
Talia: Hey, guys, you do not
want to escalate this.

21:14.580 --> 21:15.670
-No, no, no.
-Take it back.

21:17.000 --> 21:18.670
-I'm scared.
-It's okay, honey.

21:18.670 --> 21:21.580
It's okay, T. It's okay.

21:21.580 --> 21:24.710
-It's okay, honey. Don't worry.
-I'm scared.

21:24.710 --> 21:28.460
Hey, it's okay, T. I'm gonna
come visit you. I promise.

21:28.460 --> 21:30.290
We're gonna
take care of this.
Okay. Come on.
Hey, I'm talking to my brother.

21:30.290 --> 21:33.040
-I'ma come visit you, I promise.
. No.
-Just wait...

21:33.040 --> 21:34.710
I'ma come see you, T.
Wait in the car
while we finish up.

21:34.710 --> 21:37.040
You're gonna be all right.
No, I

21:37.040 --> 21:38.880
Hey, stay strong, okay?
I'ma come see you.

21:38.880 --> 21:44.460
♪♪

21:44.460 --> 21:46.330
Sgt. Grey: Explain
something to me, Lopez.

21:46.330 --> 21:49.210
I can see you two filed
a lot of evidence reports,

21:49.210 --> 21:52.750
but I can't seem to find
a single booking report.

21:52.750 --> 21:54.420
I've been instructing
Officer West

21:54.420 --> 21:56.540
about how patrol can leverage
lower-level criminals

21:56.540 --> 21:58.790
to get actual intel
on higher-level felons, sir.

21:58.790 --> 22:01.670
Perhaps earn some goodwill
prior to your Detectives exam?

22:03.420 --> 22:05.330
Officer Lopez convinced
our last suspect

22:05.330 --> 22:07.170
to give up a pretty
significant target.

22:07.170 --> 22:08.670
-Yes, sir.

22:08.670 --> 22:10.960
We have credible intel that
could get us Lawrence Abuto.

22:13.420 --> 22:15.290
Major Assault Crimes
would be thrilled

22:15.290 --> 22:17.420
to collar a weapons dealer
like Abuto.

22:17.420 --> 22:18.790
Loop them in.

22:18.790 --> 22:20.540
But, Lopez...

22:20.540 --> 22:21.880
...be careful.

22:21.880 --> 22:24.290
It's a high-reward strategy
but also high-risk.

22:24.290 --> 22:26.460
There's a real possibility
this won't pay off at all,

22:26.460 --> 22:27.670
and then all you did

22:27.670 --> 22:29.670
was let a bunch
of little crooks get away.

22:29.670 --> 22:34.170
♪♪

22:34.170 --> 22:35.830
Capt. Andersen:
I was very clear,

22:35.830 --> 22:38.920
yet you brought our VIP into an
incredibly volatile situation.

22:38.920 --> 22:40.420
It was unintentional.

22:40.420 --> 22:42.960
We had no idea from the call
how dangerous it was gonna be.

22:42.960 --> 22:46.380
And that is the only reason that
I am being pleasant right now.

22:46.380 --> 22:48.750
You're dismissed.

22:51.380 --> 22:54.790
Crazy day, huh?
Um, did you guys get in trouble?

22:54.790 --> 22:57.620
No.
Good.

22:57.620 --> 23:01.500
Look, I-I'm having a little
thing at my place tonight,

23:01.500 --> 23:04.670
and I would love it
if you'd come.

23:04.670 --> 23:06.830
I'm gonna call it a day.

23:06.830 --> 23:07.880
Thanks.

23:10.380 --> 23:11.960
She doesn't like me,
does she?

23:11.960 --> 23:14.710
Oh, she's...

23:14.710 --> 23:15.790
No.

23:15.790 --> 23:17.580
Yeah.

23:17.580 --> 23:19.670
I get that a lot.

23:19.670 --> 23:23.330
Listen, I'd really like it
if you came along tonight.

23:23.330 --> 23:27.380
It's my little way of saying
thank you for today.

23:27.380 --> 23:32.380
I really should get home,
get some rest, but...

23:32.580 --> 23:34.790
you know, someone did tell
me I need to start putting
myself out there more,

23:34.790 --> 23:37.500
so what the hell?

23:37.500 --> 23:39.580
