27:47.790 --> 27:48.880
John Nolan.
Nice to meet you.

27:48.880 --> 27:50.330
LAPD.

27:50.330 --> 27:51.670
He took me
on a ride along today.

27:51.670 --> 27:53.080
-Mm-hmm.

27:53.080 --> 27:55.620
That's so cool.
So, what's it like being a cop?

27:55.620 --> 27:57.080
Oh, God, it's amazing.

27:57.080 --> 27:58.580
